<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/logo/favicon.png">
  <title>det-AI</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;      
     background-color: #f5f2eb;
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #000000;
      position: relative;
    }

    .overlay {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }

    #logo {
      width: 50px; /* Adjust the logo size */
      height: auto;
      position: absolute;
      top: 40px;
      left: 20px;
      margin-left: 50px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .content{
      width: 100%;
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      text-align: center;
      color: #000000;
    }
    .content h1{
      font-size: 60px;
      margin-top: 80px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .content p{
        font-size: 20px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      font-weight: 100;
      line-height: 25px;
    }
    .button {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 200px;
            padding: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 10px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: 2px solid #aedddf;
            color: #000000;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .button span {
            background: #b7d9db;
            height: 100%;
            width: 0;
            border-radius: 25px;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            z-index: -1;
            transition: 0.5s;
        }

        .button:hover span {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .button:hover, .button:active {
            border: none;
        }

        .button:active span {
            background: #d9138a;
        }

        .buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="overlay"></div>
  <img id="logo" src="/logo/logo.png" alt="Logo">
  <div class="content">
    
    <p class="message">Dear User,</p>
    <p class="message">We regret to inform you that the recovery of forgotten passwords is not possible in our system.</p>
    <p class="message">In light of this, we recommend the following:</p>
    <p class="message">Create a new user ID to continue accessing our services.</p>
    <p class="message">Take a moment to recall your password, as it is crucial for your account security.</p>
    <div>
      <a href="/login" class="button"><span></span>LOG IN</a>
      <a href="/register" class="button"><span></span>SIGN UP</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
